<p>Manton mentions <a href="https://www.manton.org/2025/12/08/i-like-this-blog-post.html">he likes to work from coffee shops</a>. He doesn&rsquo;t care about the coffee&rsquo;s quality <em>that</em> much.</p>
<p>In my case, some places in the city are better than my homemade espresso, and others are worse. Those who fail this test don&rsquo;t get a second visit from me. It&rsquo;s about a 50/50 chance.</p>
